about.aboutContent:
Get Started
Click on any of the neighbourhoods to find out more about the neighbourhoods.
 To remove or add layers
 Access legend 
 Explore around you
 Direction

Toronto On Wheels is a community based application that encourages the use of sustainable transportation. 
Toronto On Wheels will allow the community to explore different neighbourhoods  and unique bicycle features to discover the city and create a pluralistic experience.
Individuals can discover potential neighbourhoods that meet their bicycle needs to acquire a better appreciation for their Toronto life.
